<div class='ui inverted segment red-accent'>
  <div class='ui top inverted secondary pointing tabular menu'>
    <a class='active item' data-tab='first'>Hotel Info</a>
    <a class='item' data-tab='second'>Venue Info</a>
  </div>

  <div class='ui active tab inverted segment' data-tab='first'>
    <div>
      <%= image_tag 'https://cache.carlsonhotels.com/ow-cms/rad/images/hotels/UTSALTLK/NewPILOT/SLCU_Overview_Exterior_630x310.jpg', class: 'ui rounded fluid image' %>
    </div>
    <div class='ui list'>
      <div class='item'>
        <div class='ui large inverted red header content'>This Really Cool Hotel</div>
      </div>
      <div class='item'>
        <i class='ui red inverted marker icon'></i>
        <div class='content'>123 Some Cool Rd. Great Town, FL 32222</div>
      </div>
      <div class='ui item'>
        <i class='ui red inverted call icon'></i>
        <div class='content'>321-555-1234</div>
      </div>
      <div class='item'>
        <div class='content'>
          Some text here about how you get a really good deal on rooms if you order before some date,
          Yadda yadda, what a great hotel.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='ui item action-items right-aligned'>
        <%= link_to '#', class: 'ui inverted red button', target: '_blank' do %>
          <i class='external icon'></i> Book Now
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='ui tab inverted segment' data-tab='second'>
    <%= link_to '#', target: '_blank' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'http://cdn.newsapi.com.au/image/v1/0a0ceda4bda18e664ffac1a8fa86a7d1', class: 'ui rounded fluid image' %>
    <% end %>
    <div class='ui list'>
      <div class='item'>
        <div class='ui large inverted red header content'>Great Town Civic Center</div>
      </div>
      <div class='item'>
        <i class='ui red inverted marker icon'></i>
        <div class='content'>482 Highway 14, Great Town, FL 32222</div>
      </div>
      <div class='ui item'>
        <i class='ui red inverted calendar icon'></i>
        <div class='content'>Feb 17, 2016 8:00am - 8:00pm</div>
      </div>
      <div class='item'>
        <div class='content'>
          The venue features free wi-fi, cables, lockers, whatever you need.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='ui item action-items right-aligned'>
        <%= link_to '#', class: 'ui inverted red button' do %>
          <i class='info circle icon'></i> More Info
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .ui.list .item.header {
    font-size: 1.5em;
  }

  .ui.item.action-items {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .ui.action-items.right-aligned {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .ui.tab.inverted.segment {
    margin-bottom: 0px;
  }
</style>